Joey,

Thanks again for the offer to introduce us to Netflix. How's the below for
some context?

"Indigometrics is a SaaS platform that provides statistical models of
employee I&D *actions* (not engagement) as evaluated anonymously by peers.
It sounds as though Netflix are making great strides in recruitment and
outreach; we'd like to help with the behavioral /cultural piece.

Put another way, we can put actual numbers on how I&D is growing and being
supported inside the company - by who, where, and when."

Let me know if that's useful; I'm happy to refine.

Separately, we had an all-hands that included *all* our team members today
and I was happily surprised to see my heartfelt outreach reciprocated. Your
advice was very well heralded and a big lesson I'll carry forward. Thanks!

Very much obliged,
- J
